            "title": "〈經濟部記者會〉「好人緣」助攻能源！龔明鑫曝多國主動援助LNG與戰備儲油 化解中東危機",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/plVDALJ_s.oOdOKU8yDHoA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/b745fb6505d2cbf1c7c0b14a18076ab3\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%BA%E7%B7%A3-%E5%8A%A9%E6%94%BB%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90-%E9%BE%94%E6%98%8E%E9%91%AB%E6%9B%9D%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9lng%E8%88%87%E6%88%B0%E5%82%99%E5%84%B2%E6%B2%B9-%E5%8C%96%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F-080536677.html",
